{"tid":52003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"這個聖誕不快樂","createTime":"2016-12-23T16:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T19:05:41.000Z","uid":68526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1409781216b717a979baa5846258af6b5ca92b38","tid":52003,"uid":68526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"Sorry唔係故<br />\n<br />\n事源<br />\n我朋友用依個AC開左個po問幫人碌左卡未還錢<br />\n我就係佢口中既朋友 當事人<br />\n大家既留言我都睇哂 我知我on9同蠢<br />\n亦都好多謝各位巴打既意見<br />\n<br />\n我已經預左果5萬要自己填<br />\n所以我借用我朋友既AC 想同大家講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認撚住依條八婆！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VZ908q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VZ908q.jpg&h=aee26a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊係佢個女<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ND38x86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FND38x86.jpg&h=60635e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rr87im8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRr87im8.jpg&h=8cf16dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初22/10 佢話佢親戚第二日要結婚 話佢唔記得左件事<br />\n要幫佢個親戚買龍鳳鈪 話25/10會還<br />\n我就勁on9咁信左 係周大福碌完之後仲送埋佢上車走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就用各種藉口拖 話銀行批左筆錢要星期六29/10 先拎到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/002854_f651443666d24fb84496cdbc359df11a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F002854_f651443666d24fb84496cdbc359df11a.jpg&h=8dd5cfc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又開埋個群組話會每日報到<br />\n唔會走我地數咁話<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j26j66L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj26j66L.jpg&h=63ea78d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/002927_65a5452e73bbbcf38f8b9d05b563b072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F002927_65a5452e73bbbcf38f8b9d05b563b072.jpg&h=84a5aa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實我另一個同事都傻仔左幫佢碌埋錢<br />\n我地兩個一共9萬幾<br />\n<br />\n我驚佢冇錢還 所以就叫佢寫借據<br />\n佢又話我唔信佢 話佢唔會呃我 一定還到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqwxqXC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqwxqXC.jpg&h=25e3c64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n29/10 佢當然冇還到啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/003331_27947e2ed97c9cf86996f7053e53e8f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F003331_27947e2ed97c9cf86996f7053e53e8f2.jpg&h=1f532ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當日佢就影左佢銀行卡既帳面數俾我地睇 成40幾萬<br />\n要星期一3點半先有得拎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7w9y7D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7w9y7D.jpg&h=d6b7ce14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知佢星期一 31/10朝早無啦啦打電話黎話要番大陸<br />\n6點前會搞掂哂<br />\n我地緊係驚佢會走數啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/340Wd0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F340Wd0n.jpg&h=33397afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最搞笑既黎料<br />\n<br />\n打住咁多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfe781400d504eaa7e97289ba3277b04b88d3da","tid":52003,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"咁仆街嘅人都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd414216f4ab041629eea09f171fe8ef7ee2c0a","tid":52003,"uid":68526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:55:29.000Z","msg":"佢01/11入左6萬幾既票俾我<br />\n話因爲佢親戚改左票冇通知佢 要即刻上去整<br />\n後來就分開票黎入<br />\n我見佢入票都知有可能會彈票<br />\n佢就好老定咁叫我等埋星期四 03/11睇下會唔會彈<br />\n仲約埋時間<br />\n當日未到3點佢就打黎話真係彈左票 連佢40幾萬都彈埋<br />\n之後佢就話要搵佢老公幫手 又話唔想俾佢老公知<br />\n但冇哂辦法先焗住講<br />\n<br />\n佢打完俾佢老公話要星期5 04/11夜晚番黎香港拆掂單野（話佢老公要番大陸做生意wor 一定會幫到佢<br />\n<br />\n點知我4號就收到銀行彈既票<br />\n屌你老母咩得果40蚊同我入6萬幾？<br />\n當時我都笑撚左<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/004411_3738e42a894bf1ea57fe668aeb6176a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F004411_3738e42a894bf1ea57fe668aeb6176a0.jpg&h=097f0324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢解釋話遲d先講 我都估到佢想話佢親戚水佢<br />\n<br />\n到左4/11話佢老公要05/11星期六 先番黎<br />\n仲話要係大陸坐5個鐘頭車黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等撚到天黑佢打黎喊住話佢老公同佢嘈離婚 <br />\n要我地send個卡數單俾佢睇係咪真係有件事<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/005011_c92b36700e144e5548b01ad9ab26d5f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F005011_c92b36700e144e5548b01ad9ab26d5f5.jpg&h=739fa970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/005355_c8551d3861888c4fa6b2e27d903b979a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F005355_c8551d3861888c4fa6b2e27d903b979a.jpg&h=946caa9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑似佢老公<br />\n（如果唔係sorry殺錯良民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRhr0BZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRhr0BZ.jpg&h=578d108e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db80d74c395178ec43162ec900c07a6dc40a06f6","tid":52003,"uid":11171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"Live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a791dd90ac92164298404050df7a96bbc38f606","tid":52003,"uid":68526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"最後總之係到拖<br />\n話佢老公過幾日有張船票到帳<br />\n（稱係公司戶口 應該幾大粒）<br />\n睇死佢地兩公婆係到玩野<br />\n所以過住d錢俾我（止渴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2mSHo0X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2mSHo0X.jpg&h=f9a989eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COP1822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOP1822.jpg&h=9b0f9224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好死唔死俾我估中<br />\n六合彩又唔見我中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來約左佢去銀行拎錢<br />\n因為佢問左UA借十萬 叫我同佢去拎票<br />\n點知放我飛機話要去荃灣搵佢老公去銀行<br />\n佢老公唔俾佢借UA wor <br />\n(聲稱佢老公做地盤)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWh3OoM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWh3OoM.jpg&h=8eaeaa56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後話排左勁耐隊先拎得一萬俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/010341_3a4d29b5c823254862f8c0c1f3bb124a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F010341_3a4d29b5c823254862f8c0c1f3bb124a.jpg&h=452b3aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後尾又問所謂既親戚借左二萬蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fa3985F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffa3985F.jpg&h=32246eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又話借左幾千 之後冇再還過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢聲稱段錄音係英利(?)財務同佢講批左筆錢 要上去補資料<br />\n話佢之前借過錢有良好記錄 一定批<br />\n總之後尾又玩票之類啦 又入票又彈票 一直拖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/010702_f8a158cdecb295539cf0e32a8356494f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F010702_f8a158cdecb295539cf0e32a8356494f.jpg&h=1dd0dcd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bf7adc7c823e1a2da2e2260d58670a4377a4319","tid":52003,"uid":68526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"講得多都口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfUxBSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyfUxBSo.jpg&h=87f37bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/011425_ab584c7a442f43285a3215d2e4fa4c08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F011425_ab584c7a442f43285a3215d2e4fa4c08.jpg&h=e147074d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又話佢有兩個朋友出花紅 每人借佢2萬5<br />\n我心諗 on9啊12月出花紅？<br />\n後尾冇數就話佢兩個朋友都搞錯哂出花紅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qi2m4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qi2m4t.jpg&h=3a85ff46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8gk889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8gk889.jpg&h=a5f7719b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連所謂既英利都彈票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/011510_087fcee8077ed4178f7bf7c5677cce04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F011510_087fcee8077ed4178f7bf7c5677cce04.jpg&h=e9191a50&s={SIZE}\" />佢又話問左個好撚有錢既朋友借5萬5<br />\n講到好唔情願咁搵 話佢個朋友要收佢息<br />\n話個朋友係沙田開公司 肯定搞得掂wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65a2L65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65a2L65.jpg&h=cb8d3433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁當然入票既野佢一定會彈票<br />\n所以又拖到我12月尾都未有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81q4vq9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81q4vq9.jpg&h=b68f45ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無啦啦問朋友借5萬5<br />\n突然變左廿幾萬<br />\n嚇撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7j1q6A7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7j1q6A7.jpg&h=3c25aed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係電話講話冬至一定搞得掂<br />\n話我地會平平安安咁過冬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/011555_d4cef6fc9986b6859a779a13f87c1828.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F011555_d4cef6fc9986b6859a779a13f87c1828.jpg&h=2ba3d5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">平你老母啊！！！！！！！！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxFT96R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxFT96R.jpg&h=42190710&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mt4943F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmt4943F.jpg&h=c98a3065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌 到最後今日冇撚聽過電話<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/012804_47e91aec5e730a617e5d403df5a7a7da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F012804_47e91aec5e730a617e5d403df5a7a7da.jpg&h=6fa8aa63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36e71f5ed2c07ecba7d5fd38b6c54206424325f5","tid":52003,"uid":68526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁仆街嘅人都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成40幾歲啊 又有老公又有個十幾歲既女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁撚仆街"},{"pid":"8e7aacd709fe763f6ef39661276bf784ed09d524","tid":52003,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:36:2